				<name type="primary" sortindex="1" value="Z Day Survivor: Per Ullus Opes" />
			
						                           
						               													<description>Z Day Survivor: Per Ullus Opes (&amp;quot;By any means&amp;quot;) is a turn based game of strategy and luck that features 8 unique characters for varying styles of play. Using a one-of-a-kind Zombie Survival Kit, track the spread of the virus, bonuses to movement, and organize items collected during your journey to become...the Z Day Survivor.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The city is cut off. No help is coming. Will you be bitten or will you fight, cheat, and steal your way to victory to become... the Z Day Survivor?  Eight survivors trapped in a hospital receive an emergency broadcast, warning that no help is coming. The only chance for survival is to escape anyway you can to an extraction point near the far edge of town. There's just one catch --- salvation is on a first come, first serve basis and seats are in short supply.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The strategy is simple: MOVE, SCAVENGE, FIGHT.  Each player enacts his turn in three phases.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Move -- Traverse the terrain as quickly as you can. It's a race to be the first to escape.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Scavenge -- Gather items and search for vehicles necessary to help you get ahead of the crowd.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Fight -- Behind each corner waits looters ready to strip you of your supplies, displaced civilians that may need your help, and zombies ready to tear at your flesh. Along the way, help or hinder your opponents, but take great care not to be bitter, the zombie virus spreads quickly and there are only a limited number of antidotes in play.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the box&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
